com.layers.app.controller

Class LiquorController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.layers.app.controller.LiquorController

  • @Controller
 @RequestMapping(value="/liquor")
 @SessionAttributes(value={"userToken","locationToken","requestToken"})
public class LiquorController
extends java.lang.Object

    Provides all the Liquor associated request handlers. Uses user session data to execute requests based on location. Controller method path URI values overlap to prevent Status 405 "Method Not Allowed" errors.

    -- example of request mapping:

    @GetMapping("/edit")
    @PostMapping("/edit")

    Implements context dependency injected interfaces to execute the request. Request handlers catch business logic thrown exceptions to assemble a proper response. Each function is documented by logging the result of each request.

    See Also:
    LiquorBusinessInterface, ScaleBusinessInterface, ILogger
